有一支特別高<br />\ntaobao 左點火coil 等到貨 希望換左無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8a7d0577152c39433dad7af5fa3c54cad03a66","tid":405791,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>空波都震<br />\n你都預係引擎入面有事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇睇下啲點火線係咪正常點到火</blockquote><br />\n度過點火coil內阻 有一支特別高<br />\ntaobao 左點火coil 等到貨 希望換左無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都應該係呢樣壞啦<br />\n不過最好快啲換<br />\n點火時間或者次序有問題唔知會唔會影響埋其他件"},{"pid":"f4f72851cec0e59558b6d1519c228aaa4d350a4e","tid":405791,"uid":1623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>空波都震<br />\n你都預係引擎入面有事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇睇下啲點火線係咪正常點到火</blockquote><br />\n度過點火coil內阻 有一支特別高<br />\ntaobao 左點火coil 等到貨 希望換左無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都應該係呢樣壞啦<br />\n不過最好快啲換<br />\n點火時間或者次序有問題唔知會唔會影響埋其他件</blockquote><br />\n我都驚呀 所以已經無揸出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換完無事寫返個包膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793fcfb4302714ece51356c0c36a4b7e86f0a356","tid":405791,"uid":60193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:28:20.000Z","msg":"有冇好大朕電油味"},{"pid":"6eb19b4f211a112bd3aa342c52e761eb2ee9bea9","tid":405791,"uid":1623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇好大朕電油味</blockquote><br />\n又唔係好覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4732b2b29e35b28c788a037c86f3fd55380b83a1","tid":405791,"uid":26449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"係咪怠速壞左？"},{"pid":"43fe30268d8